    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Legends of Elysium</strong> is a Free-To-Play strategy game combining collectible card and board game elements set in a rich fantasy world. Players build custom decks, choose heroes with unique abilities, and compete in intense, tactical battles. The game features  multiplayer PvP leagues and battlefield tournaments, offering a deep and immersive experience. Master strategic gameplay to rise through the ranks and claim victory in epic battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNIQUE BATTLE SYSTEM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214120/extras/df7c68deee97ae4e123df2ff134a5c28.poster.avif?t=1742974514\" width=800 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214120/extras/df7c68deee97ae4e123df2ff134a5c28.webm?t=1742974514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214120/extras/df7c68deee97ae4e123df2ff134a5c28.mp4?t=1742974514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in turn-based battles. Strategically build lands to control the board. Summon powerful units with unique abilities. Cast devastating spells to dominate the battlefield. Outsmart your enemy and destroy them to win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COLLECT POWERFUL CARDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214120/extras/53947ca6e864e8fcf664a7a526939bf7.poster.avif?t=1742974514\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214120/extras/53947ca6e864e8fcf664a7a526939bf7.webm?t=1742974514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214120/extras/53947ca6e864e8fcf664a7a526939bf7.mp4?t=1742974514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerful cards. Discover Legendary units and spells. Build your ultimate deck to dominate the battlefield. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong>:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic deck-building and hero customization.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP leagues and competitive tournaments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic fantasy world with diverse races and classes.</p></li></ul>",
